CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 11, 1950, pg. 1. Headline reads: "First Baptist Church, Penn Township, Is Scene Of Ceremony Uniting Miss Gaines, Mr. Hollinger"
TitMainTitle: Bride Arlene Allen Gaines Hollinger wearing satin wedding gown with sweetheart neckline and lace trimmed veil, holding prayer book with ribbons and orange blossoms, and groom Leonard Claybert Hollinger, walking down aisle in First Baptist Church
